init_text: Your entire life, you've been told you're deathly allergic to bees. You've always had people protecting you from them, be it your mother or a hired hand. Today, one slips through and lands on your shoulder. You hear a tiny voice say "Your Majesty, what are your orders?"

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: and you say "I'm not going to let you die, my Queen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I'm like "What?" and the bee says "I'm a bee, your Majesty.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: and the bee says "Yes, I'm a bee that was born with the ability to understand human speech.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I'm like "I don't know what to say" and the bee says "Just say anything, my Queen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I'm like "Okay, I want a sandwich" and the bee says "Yes, my Queen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I eat it and it tastes like the best sandwich I've ever had.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I'm like "This is amazing!" and the bee says "I'm glad you like it, my Queen."

actions.name: text-delete
actions.text: Take me to a paradise island

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It then flips its wings many times and I feel a tingling sensation.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I am so happy and I hug the bee.
